  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div><div><p>Upon reaching 20th level, you can empower yourself with the legends - whether true or exaggerated - of your great deeds. As a bonus action, you gain the following benefits for 1 hour:</p><ul><li>You are blessed with an otherworldly presence, gaining advantage on all Charisma checks.</li><li>Once on each of your turns when you make a weapon attack and miss, you can cause that attack to hit instead.</li></ul></div></div><div><div><ul><li>If you fail a saving throw, you can use your reaction to reroll it. When you use this feature to reroll a saving throw for which you are not proficient, add your proficiency modifier to the result of the new roll. You must use this new roll.</li></ul><p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a 5th-level spell slot to use it again.</p></div></div>",
